<div class="outreach-content">
	<div class="three-quarters-card-center">
		<h3>IRIS Outreach</h3>
		<img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/illinois-robotics-in-space/image/upload/c_scale,w_600/v1427732109/outreach5_stlkx3.jpg">
		<p>
			From volunteering at the First Lego Leauge to showing our robot to the community at the Orpheum Children's museum, IRIS has many outreach efforts throughout the year. Creating an awesome robot gives us the perfect opportunity to show kids and their parents the wonders of engineering. We hope that through our efforts we can inspire children to get excited about math, science, and building incredible engineering projects!
